    "long_instructions": "## Marketing Research Chat\r\n\r\nUse AI Chat to do some market research for your product or app. \r\n\r\nFocus on ideas that connect to your assigned role (e.g., name + slogan, visuals, script, or jingle).\r\n\r\n### Do This:\r\n1. Use AI Chat to do some market research for your product or app.\r\n    - What do students want or need in a product like yours?\r\n    - What problems are you trying to solve?\r\n    - Are there similar products already out there?\r\n    - Are there images or documents you can provide to AI?\r\n2. In your Activity Guide under Stage 1: Market Research, write:\r\n\t- The question or prompt you gave to AI\r\n\t- A summary of what the AI told you\r\n3. Want better results? Try asking AI about a specific audience—like middle schoolers, students with busy schedules, or students who use tech often.",
